name: "Bitey McHorrorfiend" by Richard F. Yates (Holy Fool)
description: [Liner pen on notebook page with digital embellishments and color.] It's monster season again! (My "Monster Season" runs from June thru May, with a couple of days off for early summer... Then we're back into the spooky stuff again!) Watch out for this fellow! If you see him floating down an alleyway at night, I wouldn't stop to chat! ---Richard F. Yates (Holy Fool)
